description: Step into modern living with this newly renovated two-bedroom, two-bath condo in South Boston, crafted for comfort and sustainability. Soaring ceilings and ample natural light illuminate refined finishes and elegant design. Enjoy your private rear balcony with a large slider, offering a tranquil neighborhood retreat. Insulated, energy-efficient oversized Pella windows enhance views and ensure a quiet, temperature-controlled environment. Experience the latest home comfort technology with a high-efficiency Navien boiler and central cooling system.  The luxurious primary bathroom features zen-like curbless showers, imported Italian tile, and Scandinavian-inspired accents. The modern kitchen boasts a premium Bertazonni appliance package and a custom range hood. Additional private storage keeps your home clutter-free.
